    	<h5 class="jumbotron-heading">Semantic Segmentation</h5>
    	<p class="text-muted">We provide the <a href="pdf/densecrf.pdf">derivation of the critical temperature</a> for the Dense Gaussian CRF, which is used in Section 6, together with experimental validation.</p>
        
        <p class="text-muted">A <a href="videos/MMSegmentation_short.mp4">short video</a> illustrating the advantages of the multi-modal segmentation of Section 7.3 is available. We use pairwise potentials from a Dense Gaussian CRF and unaries computed by a CNN. We generate 16 modes, from which the best is chosen by temporal consistency.</p>

